Package com.soen.riskgame.module.core.interfaces

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ArmyAction
    Interface ArmyAction to providing declaration of various methods related to army commands
    Command
    Interface Command which will be implemented to provide the functionality of all the commands present in this project
    ContinentAction
    Interface Continent to provide the basic functionality related to the entity Continent.
    CountryAction
    Interface CountryAction is the interface to provide the basic functionality related to the entity Country
    FortificationAction
    Interface to support the functionality of fortification phase
    MapPicker
    Interface to provide the functionality of choosing a particular map
    PlayerAction
    Interface to provide the functionality related to the player actions
    PlayerCommandListener
    Interface PlayerCommandListener to provide functionality of various Player commands
    ReinforceAction
    Interface ReinforceAction to support the functionality of Reinforce action
    View
    Interface View to support the functionality of view
